  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Women in assisted reproduction treatment they receive own or donated embryos and presenting
      an endometrial development less than 5 mm despite having received treatment with estrogen
      therapy knowing the clinical value of using the PRGF-Endoret therapy and endometrial level
      applications to improve endometrial thickness endometrial preparations for embryo transfer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
